builders.name: MidWest Van Builders
builders.address: 30 years and had been pondering the idea of combining work with my love for travel and photography.  The recent pandemic highlighted the realization that there is no time like the present to follow your dreams; so I purchased my van, pictured above, and got to building. I even began documenting this journey on my YouTube channel. Finally, in 2021 I launched my travel nurse career with West Virginia and the Appalachian mountains calling my name. While on assignment in WV, I was presented with the opportunity to help build out a van for someone near Connecticut.  Since then, I have retired from my love for nursing and began building out vans full-time.  There is nothing better than helping others follow their dreams and making them come true.
